  "text": "A race is that how do they get from our state? I am Rob. The race is a combination of the mind, body, spirit complexes of those of your so-called red planet and a careful series of genetical adjustments made by the guardians of that time. These entities arrived or were preserved for the experience upon your sphere by a type of birthing which is a non reproductive, but consists of preparing genetic material for the incarnation of the mind, body, spirit complexes of those entities from the red planet.",
